timeline.message:
Tries improvements

WIP on better selection of trie based on alphabet
Also some ideas on how to improve impls in TODOs

Signed-off-by: Greg Wilkins <gregw@webtide.com>

WIP

+ CaseSensitive ArrayTrie
+ Better space efficiency in big lookups
+ Better test cases

timeline.bodyText: It's certainly worth measuring the space & time difference between row sizes of 32 and 48.
timeline.author: lorban

replies.bodyText: My gut feeling is that the extra space for digits means that we can now more often just allocate the normal table and avoid the secondary larger table more often.
replies.author: gregw
